main event: Two USAF pilots observed a white circular object in the sky, described as being 3-5 feet in diameter, for a period of 15-20 minutes.
interesting points: The pilots followed the object for over 20 miles,The object displayed erratic flight patterns and maneuvers,The sighting was reported by military personnel,The object was analyzed, and initial conclusions attributed it to Mars, which indicates insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: USAF Washington Air National Guard pilots
